From 097728e288b1a6615e2f79a5a16789a2c24e1423 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: yxk <yangxiangkai@huawei.com>
Date: Wed, 7 May 2025 17:23:07 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] virtCCA supports SR-IOV of Mellanox NICs in CoDA scenarios.

virtcca inclusion
category: feature
bugzilla: https://gitee.com/openeuler/kernel/issues/IC6314

--------------------------------

We modified the mlx5 driver to route secure device access
via TMM, implemented  PF driver (in non-secure world) to
manage VFs (in secure world).

Signed-off-by: yxk <yangxiangkai@huawei.com>
---
